window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gabriel Wilder.</p> <p>Rock God.</p> <p>Voice of an angel.</p> <p>And in love with his best friend’s sister.</p> <p>Resisting Briar Ashford has been one of the hardest things he’s ever done.</p> <p>Until the one night he breaks his promise.</p> <p>Only when tragedy strikes, forgiveness slips through his fingers.</p> <p>Briar Ashford never let herself fall for her brother’s best friend.</p> <p>Until the night she did.</p> <p>She wanted to live in the shadows, writing the songs for the stars who shined the brightest—not finding a way to co-parent with the man who refuses to pick up his guitar again.</p> <p>The world is waiting for Gabriel Wilder to rise from the ashes. Only, first, he’ll have to figure out if he’s ready to finally let himself love the one woman who never knew had a claim to his heart all along.</p> <p>**Pieces of Me is a rockstar, best friend’s little sister, accidental pregnancy romance in the Wilder Brothers series featuring Gabriel and Briar. Each one can be listened to as a complete standalone. A HEA is guaranteed!**</p>"; 
